# Environment Variables for Local Development

# Supabase Configuration
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=http://localhost:54321
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# Google Gemini API Configuration
# Get your free API key from: https://ai.google.dev/
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

# Instructions:
# 1. After running `supabase start`, copy the Anon key from the terminal output
# 2. Replace 'your-anon-key-here' with the actual Anon key
# 3. Get a free Gemini API key from https://ai.google.dev/
# 4. Replace 'your-gemini-api-key-here' with your Gemini API key
# 5. Restart your development server with `npm run dev`
